Mushroom for 4

A fairly small but usable portion for four people... Tom may not like the concept of mushrooms.

28g margarine for onion, melt
47g margarine for mushrooms
1 onion, chopped
340g button mushrooms, wash and quater
1l chicken stock
1tsp parsley

blend until conceptually smooth (
	simmer 1hr with lid (
		sweat 8 minutes (
			cook til soft and translucent (margarine for onion, onion),
			button mushrooms),
		parsley,
		chicken stock))
